user.biography:
Blend, but don’t blend in. 🎨💞
✉️ business@spinandco.com

node.text: when I was back home a few weeks ago, I surprised some of the students at Arbor Hill elementary school in Albany NY. 💞 We answered questions, gave hugs, made tiktoks, delivered some @sistersapparel, made a donation, and also played Are You Smarter Than a 5th Grader? Enjoy this super cute vlog!! ☺️

node.text: the past few weeks i’ve been traveling non stop! i visited home to see my parents and film a few videos and then went right to florida for playlist live. i had the best time and got to see so many of you babes! enjoy this lil vlog!!
